Fight with me if you have the courage!
I want to show you the prowess of Zhao fist

59
00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:25.300
Get on stage now!

60
00:10:38.200 --> 00:10:39.800
Stop fighting. YuanJia!

61
00:10:44.600 --> 00:10:46.600
Stop now!

62
00:10:55.500 --> 00:10:57.800
Yeah! You've won!

63
00:10:57.900 --> 00:11:02.200
Now that you've had a taste of Zhao fist
Don't ever mention your puny Huo fist again

64
00:11:02.300 --> 00:11:05.500
I've won!

65
00:11:06.900 --> 00:11:07.500
YuanJia...

66
00:11:08.400 --> 00:11:13.000
Get up. YuanJia
Let's go now

67
00:11:14.300 --> 00:11:19.800
I swear! Huo YuanJia won't be beaten
by anybody again

68
00:11:21.100 --> 00:11:24.000
Master. you...
Let me apply some medicine for you

69
00:11:25.500 --> 00:11:29.500
Lai Fook. leave us
- Yes

70
00:11:36.200 --> 00:11:39.400
What happened? Angry?

71
00:11:39.500 --> 00:11:42.600
Mum. why won't Father let me learn martial arts?

72
00:11:42.700 --> 00:11:47.400
This is because he loves you
You were born with asthma

73
00:11:47.400 --> 00:11:49.800
