No. I can't
- Let me have it. will you?

121
00:15:50.200 --> 00:15:51.400
No. I will not

122
00:15:51.400 --> 00:15:55.500
Then. what do I have to do to have it?
- You can only have it after your victory today

123
00:15:55.600 --> 00:15:57.100
Really?
- Emm

124
00:15:57.100 --> 00:15:59.800
Is that a promise?

125
00:16:01.500 --> 00:16:05.200
"1900. Tian Jin"

126
00:16:12.000 --> 00:16:14.200
We're counting on you. Master Huo!

127
00:16:14.300 --> 00:16:20.200
Master Huo!
- When will you become No.1 in Tian Jin?

128
00:16:20.500 --> 00:16:25.700
I don't know and what do you think?
- It will be today! today!

129
00:16:26.900 --> 00:16:28.200
Master Huo...

130
00:16:45.200 --> 00:16:48.200
