140
00:18:50.300 --> 00:18:55.100
Well. I'll give you a chance
...to lose!

141
00:19:20.600 --> 00:19:22.600
Well done!

142
00:19:24.500 --> 00:19:26.500
Pussy claw?
- It's Tiger Claw!!

143
00:19:43.200 --> 00:19:45.500
Go down!

144
00:19:48.800 --> 00:19:51.700
Well done. master!

145
00:19:51.800 --> 00:19:53.000
Just because you wanted me to fall
doesn't mean I will have to comply ...

146
00:19:53.000 --> 00:19:56.800
Pussy claw definitely.
- It's Tiger Claw!!!!

147
00:20:14.400 --> 00:20:16.300
You're going to lose!

148
00:20:26.200 --> 00:20:28.100
Be careful

149
00:20:31.400 --> 00:20:32.600
Master...!

150
00:20:35.300 --> 00:20:36.400
Master!

151
00:20:36.800 --> 00:20:38.400
Are you alright?
- I'm fine

152
00:20:39.400 --> 00:20:40.600
What a tough guy

153
00:20:44.800 --> 00:20:46.800
Don't touch me
- And our winner is...

154
00:20:46.900 --> 00:20:48.100
Huo YuanJia!

155
00:20:48.200 --> 00:20:53.000
That was excellent. master
- Well. of course.

156
00:20:53.300 --> 00:20:56.100
Thank you everyone..

157
00:21:03.100 --> 00:21:04.300
Congratulations. this way

158
00:21:04.300 --> 00:21:05.900
Good Job. Master Huo
- Thank you

159
00:21:06.400 --> 00:21:09.500
We have reserved a table for you upstairs. Master Huo

160
00:21:09.500 --> 00:21:10.300
All right...

161
00:21:10.600 --> 00:21:11.500
YuanJia!

162
00:21:11.500 --> 00:21:12.900
Jing Soon

163
00:21:15.400 --> 00:21:16.300
Why so late?

164
00:21:16.300 --> 00:21:17.700
let's go to our usual place

165
00:21:18.900 --> 00:21:21.400
Congratulations. Master Huo!

166
00:21:21.400 --> 00:21:23.300
Congratulations. Master Huo!

167
00:21:23.300 --> 00:21:26.800
Hello. everybody

168
00:21:29.200 --> 00:21:30.600
Come on. now

169
00:21:33.700 --> 00:21:34.700
Jing Soon

170
00:21:34.700 --> 00:21:37.600
Your GuYue resturant is becoming more and more popular

171
00:21:37.600 --> 00:21:39.100
This is all due to support I've gotten from friends

172
00:21:39.100 --> 00:21:41.700
Still remember when we were kids?

173
00:21:41.900 --> 00:21:43.700
You were a bookworm..

174
00:21:43.700 --> 00:21:46.500
I never expect you could excel in business!

175
00:21:46.600 --> 00:21:48.400
Times is really bad

176
00:21:48.400 --> 00:21:50.600
A bookworm like me can only run some small business like this

177
00:21:50.600 --> 00:21:52.500
I don't have much choices. do I?

178
00:21:52.500 --> 00:21:55.200
Help yourself. YuanJia

179
00:21:55.400 --> 00:21:58.400
These were prepared by culinary masters from this region

180
00:21:58.400 --> 00:22:00.300
Come and enjoy these delicious dishes

181
00:22:00.300 --> 00:22:02.300
All right. let's dig in

182
00:22:02.400 --> 00:22:05.900
After you. Master Huo

183
