510
01:17:03.800 --> 01:17:05.500
See if this is what you wanted

511
01:17:06.700 --> 01:17:10.100
School of JingWu has 3 objectives

512
01:17:10.200 --> 01:17:16.000
Educate body. wisdom and morals
Martial arts is the way to become stronger

513
01:17:16.100 --> 01:17:18.600
There will be no segregration of clans

514
01:17:18.700 --> 01:17:23.000
Only through the exchange of arts
will one improve oneself

515
01:17:23.100 --> 01:17:25.700
By having a healthy body and alert mind

516
01:17:25.800 --> 01:17:28.500
Our people will be able to prosper again

517
01:17:28.600 --> 01:17:33.700
We shall not harm the innocent
We shall not abuse our martial arts

518
01:17:33.800 --> 01:17:38.500
Virtue and morality will be our motto
To constantly strive to better ourselves!

519
01:17:38.600 --> 01:17:42.700
"School of JingWu established in 1910"
- Ready!

520
01:17:45.500 --> 01:17:49.000
"Shanghai Foreign Chamber of Commerce"

521
01:19:06.900 --> 01:19:08.200
Yuan Jia

522
01:19:09.500 --> 01:19:13.700
Among the competitors ...
There is a Japanese man known as "Anno Tanaka"

523
01:19:13.700 --> 01:19:19.900
He likes to meet you
I heard that he is an excellent fighter

524
01:19:20.000 --> 01:19:24.400
We can only improve by fighting with the best

525
01:19:24.500 --> 01:19:29.300
Yuan Jia. this challenge from the foreigners
I don't think it's that simple

526
01:19:29.300 --> 01:19:33.200
If not why would they want you
to take on 4 fighters at once

527
01:19:33.200 --> 01:19:37.200
I guess they would try to make use 
of this opportunity to weaken our morale

528
01:19:37.200 --> 01:19:41.400
So that our school will lose its
influence in Shanghai

529
01:19:41.800 --> 01:19:46.500
Indeed. and we must win all four
matches to conclude the challenge

530
01:19:46.600 --> 01:19:49.700
It is not fair at all

531
01:19:50.000 --> 01:19:52.100
But as we live

532
01:19:52.200 --> 01:19:58.000
Who can say that all matters in life are fair

533
01:19:58.100 --> 01:20:01.400
For School of JingWu

534
01:20:01.500 --> 01:20:03.400
I have no other options

535
01:20:03.500 --> 01:20:04.700
But what if...

536
01:20:05.700 --> 01:20:08.000
Jing Soon!

537
01:20:08.100 --> 01:20:09.500
I have something to discuss with you

538
01:20:09.600 --> 01:20:11.400
What is it about?

539
01:20:11.500 --> 01:20:13.000
After this challenge

540
01:20:13.100 --> 01:20:15.100
I want you to become the next president

541
01:20:15.200 --> 01:20:18.000
Why?

542
01:20:18.200 --> 01:20:21.100
I want to take some time off to visit YueChi

543
01:20:21.600 --> 01:20:24.400
I've made a promise

544
01:20:31.700 --> 01:20:37.700
Can I conclude that you have no knowledge of tea 

545
01:20:37.800 --> 01:20:41.200
Not that I don't understand 
I'm just unwilling..

546
01:20:41.300 --> 01:20:45.600
I don't want to rank the tea
I am fine as long as it's tea 

547
01:20:45.700 --> 01:20:51.600
But tea has smell and grade

548
01:20:51.700 --> 01:20:55.400
What is good? What is bad?

549
01:20:55.500 --> 01:20:58.900
They all grow in nature
Without rank or distinction

550
01:20:59.000 --> 01:21:02.400
It's seem that you still have not understood

551
01:21:02.500 --> 01:21:05.300
Otherwise nature will determine a rank

552
01:21:05.400 --> 01:21:07.000
You are right

553
01:21:07.100 --> 01:21:09.200
So I realized that

554
01:21:09.300 --> 01:21:11.000
The quality of tea

555
01:21:11.100 --> 01:21:13.700
is not from the tea itself

556
01:21:13.800 --> 01:21:15.700
It's decided by people

557
01:21:15.800 --> 01:21:18.200
Different people have different choices

558
01:21:18.300 --> 01:21:20.300
I'm unwilling to choose this

559
01:21:20.400 --> 01:21:23.200
Oh. why?

560
01:21:23.300 --> 01:21:25.200
Appreciating tea depend on your emotion

561
01:21:25.300 --> 01:21:27.800
If you're happy

562
01:21:27.900 --> 01:21:30.700
Does the quality of tea matter?

563
01:21:30.700 --> 01:21:33.100
Oh. I've never thought of that

564
01:21:33.200 --> 01:21:37.500
According from Sir. there are numerous factions of martial arts

565
01:21:37.600 --> 01:21:41.400
Is it true there is no superiority or inferiority?

566
01:21:41.500 --> 01:21:44.100
Yes. those are my sendiments..

567
01:21:44.200 --> 01:21:47.800
In that case. I would like to pose a question to you

568
01:21:47.900 --> 01:21:50.400
Since there are no differences between martial arts

569
01:21:50.500 --> 01:21:52.600
Why are there competitions in martial arts

570
01:21:52.700 --> 01:21:57.500
I meant that all martial arts are equal

571
01:21:57.600 --> 01:22:00.800
It's the disgression of a person to manifest the art

572
01:22:00.900 --> 01:22:05.500
We can further improve through competitions 
and to discover one's true self

573
01:22:05.600 --> 01:22:09.500
Finally the real opponent is ourselves

574
01:22:09.600 --> 01:22:13.700
Only through competition.
can one recognise one's true self

575
01:22:13.800 --> 01:22:15.500
Is that you meant?

576
01:22:15.600 --> 01:22:21.600
The worst fight is with oneself

577
01:22:28.200 --> 01:22:33.800
I'm honored to having this conversation with you

578
01:22:33.900 --> 01:22:37.500
Our aim is to appreciate tea

579
01:22:37.600 --> 01:22:40.800
Let's not talk further and forget about the tea

580
01:22:40.900 --> 01:22:45.000
Come. try the tea
- Yes. the tea

581
01:22:49.300 --> 01:22:54.000
"1910. Shanghai"

582
01:22:57.000 --> 01:23:00.500
"Theater Biarya. French territory"

583
01:23:01.600 --> 01:23:04.400
"The competition at the arena"

584
01:23:11.300 --> 01:23:12.600
Ladies and gentlmen

585
01:23:12.700 --> 01:23:14.200
The last fight of the day

586
01:23:14.300 --> 01:23:16.900
Anno Tanaka from Japan

587
01:23:17.000 --> 01:23:20.500
Versus Huo YuanJia from School of JingWu

588
01:23:20.600 --> 01:23:22.500
What's the matter?

589
01:23:23.600 --> 01:23:26.900
One versus four?

590
01:23:27.000 --> 01:23:29.000
Why don't you tell me before?

591
01:23:29.100 --> 01:23:32.600
We have discussed this before

592
01:23:32.700 --> 01:23:34.200
You need not be surprised

593
01:23:34.300 --> 01:23:37.500
Is this a competition?

594
01:23:37.600 --> 01:23:41.800
This is murder!
- You worry unnecessarily

595
01:23:41.900 --> 01:23:43.500
Huo YuanJia is King of Arena

596
01:23:43.600 --> 01:23:47.600
Outstanding fighters from all over the country
were arranged to meet him today...

597
01:23:47.700 --> 01:23:50.000
San Tian

598
01:23:50.100 --> 01:23:53.100
What are you?

599
01:23:53.200 --> 01:23:55.100
Is this for the honor of Japan?

600
01:23:55.200 --> 01:23:58.500
Or is it for personal gain?

601
01:23:58.600 --> 01:24:04.400
For me. martial art is important

602
01:24:04.500 --> 01:24:08.500
Your mission is to win this competition

603
01:24:22.400 --> 01:24:24.400
Let's start!

604
01:24:24.500 --> 01:24:28.600
Brother Yuan Jia
- This competition is unfair to you

605
01:24:28.600 --> 01:24:34.300
I have no objections
If you choose to fight on another day

606
01:24:34.400 --> 01:24:36.500
I appreciate your good intentions

607
01:24:36.600 --> 01:24:41.400
But since I am already standing in this arena
There must be a conclusion to the match

608
01:24:41.500 --> 01:24:43.400
Please!

609
01:24:59.800 --> 01:25:02.600
Start!

610
01:26:06.700 --> 01:26:07.800
Good. very good

611
01:26:07.900 --> 01:26:10.200
Excellent. master!

612
01:26:52.200 --> 01:26:58.000
A draw. next round will be unarmed combat

613
01:26:58.100 --> 01:27:02.100
Both sides please prepare yourselves..

614
01:28:02.000 --> 01:28:07.200
YuanJia!

615
01:28:15.100 --> 01:28:18.400
Stop!
- What happen?

616
01:28:18.500 --> 01:28:23.600
Tanaka. why stop fighting?

617
01:28:23.700 --> 01:28:24.800
Yuan Jia!

618
01:28:24.900 --> 01:28:27.500
Tanaka!
- Go

619
01:28:31.700 --> 01:28:34.300
Yuan Jia. what happen?

620
01:28:34.300 --> 01:28:35.500
How are you?

621
01:28:35.600 --> 01:28:38.000
I've been poisoned..
- Poisoned?!

622
01:28:38.100 --> 01:28:39.900
How can it be?

623
01:28:39.900 --> 01:28:42.100
What did it happen?

624
01:28:42.200 --> 01:28:44.200
What are you doing?
- Water!

625
01:28:44.300 --> 01:28:45.500
Your cup!

626
01:28:45.600 --> 01:28:47.300
What happen to your drink?

627
01:28:47.400 --> 01:28:49.500
There is poison in the drink!

628
01:28:49.600 --> 01:28:52.300
The evidence has been removed already
Yuan Jia. let's go to hospital

629
01:28:52.400 --> 01:28:54.400
Master. we go to hospital

630
01:28:54.400 --> 01:28:56.700
I've over-exerted myself

631
01:28:56.800 --> 01:29:03.600
Too late. the poison is making its way to my heart
- Master. I will revenge you...

632
01:29:03.700 --> 01:29:13.300
Zhen Sheng!
You should not be seeking revenge 

633
01:29:13.400 --> 01:29:19.000
Hatred will beget hatred

634
01:29:19.100 --> 01:29:23.100
I don't want to see these hatred

635
01:29:23.200 --> 01:29:26.500
What is important is strengthen one's self
- Yuan Jia!

636
01:29:26.600 --> 01:29:29.700
Master
- Yuan Jia. let's stop the fight

637
01:29:29.800 --> 01:29:36.200
I will send you to hospital. let's go
- Jing Soon!

638
01:29:36.300 --> 01:29:40.600
I'm just a brute fighter

639
01:29:41.600 --> 01:29:46.900
I took many years to understand what martial arts is

640
01:29:47.000 --> 01:29:53.100
and what I have done with it?
This competition not yet to finish

641
01:29:53.200 --> 01:29:59.100
We can't choose the life they wanted

642
01:29:59.200 --> 01:30:04.700
But we must have the courage to finish it

643
01:30:08.300 --> 01:30:09.900
Master...

644
01:30:10.000 --> 01:30:14.500
What are you doing?
- What do you mean?

645
01:30:14.600 --> 01:30:15.700
You ask too many questions!

646
01:30:15.800 --> 01:30:20.400
(I must win this fight)
Just win this competition!

647
01:30:29.600 --> 01:30:40.000
Constantly strive to better oneself!

648
01:30:40.100 --> 01:30:43.000
See for yourself...

649
01:31:00.100 --> 01:31:01.600
Don't fight

650
01:31:01.700 --> 01:31:06.400
Staying alive is most important

651
01:31:06.500 --> 01:31:16.600
Listen.
Living is not just for one person

652
01:31:16.700 --> 01:31:22.700
If we must fight. I will not hold back

653
01:31:22.800 --> 01:31:24.500
This will be my honor

654
01:33:21.600 --> 01:33:23.800
Master...

655
01:33:38.100 --> 01:33:40.400
Wait!

656
01:34:01.300 --> 01:34:02.400
Huo

657
01:34:02.500 --> 01:34:03.600
Yuan

658
01:34:03.700 --> 01:34:04.900
Jia

659
01:34:05.000 --> 01:34:06.300
Yuan Jia!

660
01:34:06.400 --> 01:34:09.800
Huo Yuan Jia...
- Huo Yuan Jia...

661
01:34:09.900 --> 01:34:11.300
Master!

662
01:34:11.400 --> 01:34:23.500
Huo Yuan Jia...
- Huo Yuan Jia...

663
01:34:23.600 --> 01:34:24.800
Master!

664
01:34:27.000 --> 01:34:29.800
Tanaka. see what have you done!

665
01:34:29.900 --> 01:34:32.800
I've lost!
- Say who and witnessed by who?

666
01:34:32.900 --> 01:34:35.000
I saw it myself

667
01:34:35.100 --> 01:34:38.600
I've lost by virtue of martial art ethics
- Who are you to decide?

668
01:34:38.700 --> 01:34:43.200
How can you make decisions just like that?

669
01:34:49.900 --> 01:34:52.000
San Tian

670
01:34:52.000 --> 01:34:55.900
You're an embarrassment to Japan

671
01:36:55.000 --> 01:37:01.500
Huo YuanJia died shortly after arriving 
at the hospital. he was only 42 years old

672
01:37:01.600 --> 01:37:05.600
After his death. his teachings have 
continued to flourish among the people. 

673
01:37:05.700 --> 01:37:09.500
To date. the school has established 
internationally in over 50 countries...

674
01:37:09.600 --> 01:37:13.100
Dr. Sun YatSen has written these words 
in memory of Huo YuanJia's aspirations

675
01:37:13.200 --> 01:37:18.100
"Essence of learning martial arts"

